      "role": "user",
      "content": "i don't even think i can do this anymore. the lab results just came back and it's another dead end. after 5 years, i've got nothing to show for it. my advisor won't even look me in the eye and the funding is basically gone. i'm just so cosmically tired of fighting for something that doesn't even want me. i feel like i'm just running on empty and there's no way to refill it.",
