      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. but it doesn't feel like a \"step back\" would fix it. taking a vacation or a break just feels like delaying the inevitable. like, the truth is my career is dead and the person i thought i was is gone. i'm just stuck in this loop of failing and feeling like a burden to everyone around me. i just want the noise to stop. i just want to rest, truly rest, without everything constantly weighing me down.",
